parameters:
\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0], you've come this
far... and now, prepare for some destruction and
slaughter...

It seems like \C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0] did as
they pleased...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0], we must completely
control this land... For that, we need to dominate
all regions...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0] Konoha... If it's you,
you should be able to do it...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0], now, unleash your
tyranny upon humanity... and let us dominate
everything, together, and build a new Demon
realm...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0], now go... We must not
grant a future to those mediocre creatures called
humans...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0]\C[3] will exterminate
all Lolimon leaders and invade the Reingarnet...

\C[10]Demon God Devill\C[0], however, it seems
that you have not yet transformed into a Devil
Witch... Bear our child and give birth to it...

\C[10]The condition to become a Devil Witch
is...\C[0].

Entered the Evil Route and withdrew from the
Magical Girl Guild.
